extend layout

block content
  main.page.projects-page
  section.portfolio-block.projects-cards
    .container
      .heading
        h5 Parties need music. Just with some simple steps, you are free to enjoy the party with music on.
      .row.justify-content-center
        .col-md-6.col-lg-6
          .card.border-0
            a(href='#')
              img.guide.card-img-top(src='/images/guide_login.gif' alt='Card Image')
            .card-body
              h6
                a(href='#') Login
              p.text-muted.card-text The authentication is done with Spotify. The application only saves your access_token to serve your needs. You can withdraw these rights with Spotify application.
        .col-md-6.col-lg-6
          .card.border-0
            a(href='#')
              img.guide.card-img-top(src='/images/guide_createroom.gif' alt='Card Image')
            .card-body
              h6
                a(href='#') Create Room and Start the party
              p.text-muted.card-text You can load top 10 songs (in real time) from all other rooms or search for songs (from Spotify) as suggestion for your party. Click Start the party then Enjoy the music.
      
      .heading  
        h6 Wait. How about your friends? It's time for them to vote.
      .row.justify-content-center
        .col-md-6.col-lg-6
          .card.border-0
            a(href='#')
              img.guide.card-img-top(src='/images/guide_users.gif' alt='Card Image')
            .card-body
              h6
                a(href='#') Vote for songs you like.
              p.text-muted.card-text Your friends access the website, enter your room, search and vote for songs.
        

        
